children.subject: In my opinion, this is a lot. 16B with Sahai..will be a lot of HW. 61B with Hilfinger is going to be a lot of project work. So, be careful. I had these 2 techs along with one more tech and 1 breadth and it was very busy.

Very bad idea if you have never had a 4-tech + breadth semester before because upper divs like 126 and 127 can be much more time consuming than let's say 61A. Don't do it especially if you have not taken and did well in CS 70 (both 126 and 188 pretty much needs it).
